Two trains have collided at the Van Riebeeckpark Station in Kempton Park on Thursday afternoon. Metrorail spokesperson Lilian Mofokeng confirmed the incident. “There was a collision that happened at Van Riebeeckpark station. I do not have any further details at the moment as I am rushing to the scene‚" Mofokeng said. The number and nature of the injuries is not yet known. This is a developing story.